				<td colspan="2"><span>Have you ever noticed that you can oftne START a song from just outside the doors?  That is because not only are the mobs within range, they are also within line of sight.
<br />

<br />
Nro dungeons are notorious for this.  I often open the doors from as FAR away as I can to avoid being jumped.  I then lull whatever i can see in the room, creeping forward at angles for each one.  Often, my first pull ends up being whatever jumps me when I get close to the door.</span></td>
